              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "libxml: Heap use after free (UAF) leads to Denial of service (DoS)"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A use-after-free vulnerability was found in libxml2. This issue occurs when parsing XPath elements under certain circumstances when the XML schematron has the \u003csch:name path=\"...\"/\u003e schema elements. This flaw allows a malicious actor to craft a malicious XML document used as input for libxml, resulting in the program's crash using libxml or other possible undefined behaviors."
